  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE AN INCOME TAX CREDIT, IN AN AMOUNT NOT TO EXCEED $25,000.00 ANNUALLY PER TAXPAYER, FOR CONTRIBUTIONS TO ONE OR MORE STATE INSTITUTIONS OF HIGHER LEARNING; TO PROVIDE THAT ANY UNUSED PORTION OF THE CREDIT MAY BE CARRIED FORWARD FOR THE FIVE SUCCEEDING TAX YEARS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
